{"tid":437974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥承諾　騰出空間讓學生發夢","createTime":"2017-10-16T12:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T13:27:01.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a1d8d5d24021ef45c90d0e8bd41ba6f1aece13","tid":437974,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥出席網台直播節目，就施政報告與學生對談交流，又回答來自學校和社區網絡的網上提問。<br />\n<br />\n有學生提及政府在創意產業上的問題，林鄭月娥說，會研究課程是否阻礙學生創意思維，會騰出空間讓學生發夢，培育創意。<br />\n<br />\n有學生關注本港房屋政策能否參考新加坡，林鄭月娥形容房屋問題是「牽一髮而動全身」，施政報告著墨較多，但需要有土地。<br />\n<br />\n她以「麵包」及「麵粉」比喻房屋及土地，如果欠缺「麵粉」，房屋政策「都係得個講字」，政府會積極探討土地來源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1359511-20171016.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1359511-20171016.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=iHe0AXGv8ycdxYU%2FahLYxwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=b819e1fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1359511-20171016.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e1a59be5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1359511-20171016.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e17ee69f16aedabaa9dc9fe8366ef0bcb4e399ed","tid":437974,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:02:41.000Z","msg":"發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b806e0ce799d796122e0e20dee1320776e86baba","tid":437974,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行政長官林鄭月娥出席網台直播節目，就施政報告與學生對談交流，又回答來自學校和社區網絡的網上提問。<br />\n<br />\n有學生提及政府在創意產業上的問題，林鄭月娥說，會研究課程是否阻礙學生創意思維，會騰出空間讓學生發夢，培育創意。<br />\n<br />\n有學生關注本港房屋政策能否參考新加坡，林鄭月娥形容房屋問題是「牽一髮而動全身」，施政報告著墨較多，但需要有土地。<br />\n<br />\n她以「麵包」及「麵粉」比喻房屋及土地，如果欠缺「麵粉」，房屋政策「都係得個講字」，政府會積極探討土地來源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1359511-20171016.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1359511-20171016.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=iHe0AXGv8ycdxYU%2FahLYxwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=b819e1fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1359511-20171016.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e1a59be5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1359511-20171016.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a></blockquote><br />\n而家大撚把麵粉啦, 係佢地夾硬用黎整貴價蛋糕姐"},{"pid":"e3714f281677b65ce57c48283f791e3adf9227f1","tid":437974,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都叫有一張床發夢嘅，未死得住"}]}